Welcome to Eastern Stories!!
 
A note for English Only user:
Eastern Stories supports both Chinese and English messages, but as you
can see, most English messages are not complete yet and some of the
messages are not complete. If you got stuck because of message problem,
feel free to holler.
 
Non-Chinese speaking users: You might found this mud hard to understand,
that's because the users here are mostly from Taiwan. If you have
questions, feel free to ask around but remember to inform them that you
can't read Chinese.
 
Suggestions/Corrections on English texts please notify the translate domain
crews. (That's Elon & Platino for now)
 
